# 4D Persona Implementation Progress

**Started**: 2025-12-31
**Completed**: 2025-12-31
**Status**: COMPLETE

---

## User Requirements (CONFIRMED)

| Requirement | Choice | Implementation |
|-------------|--------|----------------|
| Live Data | A - Real-time | Mood from football-data.org API |
| Dialects | B - Regional | North/Midlands/London/South groupings |
| Rivalry Source | A - Use KG | Existing edge weights from soccer_ai_kg.db |
| Breaking Changes | B - Feature flag | `USE_4D_PERSONA = True/False` |
| Anti-Gaslighting | B - Implicit | Natural fan defense, no technical citations |
| Conversation Topics | C - Weave naturally | Injuries/transfers/fixtures based on context |

---

## What We're Building

**The Vision**: Transform Robert from "costume" to "computed position"

- **BEFORE**: Mood is a string, declared, easily gaslighted
- **AFTER**: Mood is COMPUTED from live match results, has provenance

The 4D Position: `P(t) = (x, y, z, t)`
- **X (Emotional)**: Win 3-0 -> euphoric, Loss to rival -> devastated
- **Y (Relational)**: Mention Everton to Liverpool fan -> rivalry mode
- **Z (Linguistic)**: Liverpool -> Northern dialect
- **T (Temporal)**: Conversation trajectory, memory, momentum

Conversation topics (injuries, transfers, fixtures) are woven NATURALLY based on context, not forced.

